: 1361, \"to\": 1442, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"upstream and downstream buoys\", \"from\": 1376, \"to\": 1405}, {\"ngram\": \"a mandatory kayak roll\", \"from\": 1419, \"to\": 1441}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is a full contact sport too, dodgems for canoes, featuring no points for style.\", \"from\": 1444, \"to\": 1528, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a full contact sport\", \"from\": 1452, \"to\": 1472}, {\"ngram\": \"dodgems\", \"from\": 1478, \"to\": 1485}, {\"ngram\": \"canoes\", \"from\": 1490, \"to\": 1496}, {\"ngram\": \"no points\", \"from\": 1508, \"to\": 1517}, {\"ngram\": \"style\", \"from\": 1522, \"to\": 1527}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's winner-takes-all with a high bar in the risk and reward ratio,as both Clarke and Woods can testify.\", \"from\": 1529, \"to\": 1633, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a high bar\", \"from\": 1556, \"to\": 1566}, {\"ngram\": \"the risk\", \"from\": 1570, \"to\": 1578}, {\"ngram\": \"ratio\", \"from\": 1590, \"to\": 1595}, {\"ngram\": \"both Clarke\", \"from\": 1599, \"to\": 1610}, {\"ngram\": \"Woods\", \"from\": 1615, \"to\": 1620}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Formerly known as extreme slalom, the International Canoe Federation had campaigned for its inclusion at the Games since the format made its debut in 2015.\", \"from\": 1635, \"to\": 1790, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1673, \"end\": 1703, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Canoe_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Canoe Federation\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Canoe_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Canoe_Federation\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"extreme slalom\", \"from\": 1653, \"to\": 1667}, {\"ngram\": \"its inclusion\", \"from\": 1723, \"to\": 1736}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1740, \"to\": 1749}, {\"ngram\": \"the format\", \"from\": 1756, \"to\": 1766}, {\"ngram\": \"its debut\", \"from\": 1772, \"to\": 1781}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And they have a hit on their hands and extreme it is.\", \"from\": 1792, \"to\": 1845, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a hit\", \"from\": 1806, \"to\": 1811}, {\"ngram\": \"their hands\", \"from\": 1815, \"to\": 1826}, {\"ngram\": \"extreme\", \"from\": 1831, \"to\": 1838}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If modern pentathlon is looking toNinja Warriorfor inspiration for the latest iteration of their sport, the officials at the ICF have clearly been watching You Tube videos ofIt's a Knockout.\", \"from\": 1846, \"to\": 2036, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1971, \"end\": 1974, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Canoe_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7124468784301026e-26, \"text\": \"ICF\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Canoe_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Canoe_Federation\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"modern pentathlon\", \"from\": 1849, \"to\": 1866}, {\"ngram\": \"toNinja Warriorfor inspiration\", \"from\": 1878, \"to\": 1908}, {\"ngram\": \"the latest iteration\", \"from\": 1913, \"to\": 1933}, {\"ngram\": \"their sport\", \"from\": 1937, \"to\": 1948}, {\"ngram\": \"the officials\", \"from\": 1950, \"to\": 1963}, {\"ngram\": \"ofIt\", \"from\": 2018, \"to\": 2022}, {\"ngram\": \"a Knockout\", \"from\": 2025, \"to\": 2035}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Clarke won slalom gold on his Olympic debut eight years ago but was controversially not selected to defend his title in Tokyo, contemplating walking away from the sport.\", \"from\": 2038, \"to\": 2207, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2158, \"end\": 2163, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.8954767346478469, \"rank\": 0.11672029956567818, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Clarke\", \"from\": 2038, \"to\": 2044}, {\"ngram\": \"slalom gold\", \"from\": 2049, \"to\": 2060}, {\"ngram\": \"his Olympic debut\", \"from\": 2064, \"to\": 2081}, {\"ngram\": \"his title\", \"from\": 2145, \"to\": 2154}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 2197, \"to\": 2206}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Woods has spoken candidly abouther difficult relationship with mental health, which has been as choppy as the water she paddles on for as long as she can remember.\", \"from\": 2209, \"to\": 2372, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Woods\", \"from\": 2209, \"to\": 2214}, {\"ngram\": \"abouther difficult relationship\", \"from\": 2235, \"to\": 2266}, {\"ngram\": \"mental health\", \"from\": 2272, \"to\": 2285}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 2315, \"to\": 2324}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Clarke had looked imperious in qualifying but was badly cut up by Germany's Noah Hegge at the start, needing to summon all his racing smarts to surge from fourth to second, as New Zealand's Finn Butcher surged clear to take gold.\", \"from\": 2374, \"to\": 2603, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2440, \"end\": 2447, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8195751452629179, \"rank\": 0.21322967228873763, \"text\": \"Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2550, \"end\": 2561, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9831026975110398, \"rank\": 0.016816517195286707, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_