ome and the enjoyment factor is still there.\", \"from\": 3317, \"to\": 3391, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the enjoyment factor\", \"from\": 3355, \"to\": 3375}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When that goes then we will stop but right now I am loving life.\", \"from\": 3392, \"to\": 3456, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 3451, \"to\": 3455}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I lot did not go my way in that final, which is just what this sport is like.\", \"from\": 3458, \"to\": 3536, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"I lot\", \"from\": 3459, \"to\": 3464}, {\"ngram\": \"this sport\", \"from\": 3517, \"to\": 3527}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Silver feels like a win with the hand I was dealt in that final.\", \"from\": 3537, \"to\": 3601, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Silver\", \"from\": 3537, \"to\": 3543}, {\"ngram\": \"a win\", \"from\": 3555, \"to\": 3560}, {\"ngram\": \"the hand\", \"from\": 3566, \"to\": 3574}, {\"ngram\": \"that final\", \"from\": 3590, \"to\": 3600}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am biased when I say this, but I think kayaking is the best sport in the world and kayak cross will get kayaking out there to the masses like it needs to do.\", \"from\": 3603, \"to\": 3763, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3689, \"end\": 3694, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kayak\", \"score\": 0.999999999994543, \"rank\": 5.2596068011435584e-12, \"text\": \"kayak\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kayak\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kayak\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the best sport\", \"from\": 3657, \"to\": 3671}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 3675, \"to\": 3684}, {\"ngram\": \"the masses\", \"from\": 3732, \"to\": 3742}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's great for TV and there is lots of things we can do to propel that and get more bottoms in boats and make the sport bigger.\", \"from\": 3765, \"to\": 3893, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"TV\", \"from\": 3781, \"to\": 3783}, {\"ngram\": \"lots\", \"from\": 3797, \"to\": 3801}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 3805, \"to\": 3811}, {\"ngram\": \"more bottoms\", \"from\": 3845, \"to\": 3857}, {\"ngram\": \"boats\", \"from\": 3861, \"to\": 3866}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 3876, \"to\": 3885}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was an absolute spectacle, if you were watching on TV, you'd have given anything to be here.\\\"\", \"from\": 3894, \"to\": 3990, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an absolute spectacle\", \"from\": 3901, \"to\": 3922}, {\"ngram\": \"TV\", \"from\": 3948, \"to\": 3950}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 3969, \"to\": 3977}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Woods had already won bronze in the women's canoe slalom and made a storming start to her final, having looked unstoppable during qualifying.\", \"from\": 3992, \"to\": 4133, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Woods\", \"from\": 3992, \"to\": 3997}, {\"ngram\": \"bronze\", \"from\": 4014, \"to\": 4020}, {\"ngram\": \"the women's canoe slalom\", \"from\": 4024, \"to\": 4048}, {\"ngram\": \"a storming start\", \"from\": 4058, \"to\": 4074}, {\"ngram\": \"qualifying\", \"from\": 4122, \"to\": 4132}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She dropped in first and raced into an early lead.\", \"from\": 4135, \"to\": 4185, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an early lead\", \"from\": 4171, \"to\": 4184}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the tide turned against her, and she went from first to fourth, crossing the line devastated only to learn Germany's Elena Lilik had committed a penalty.\", \"from\": 4186, \"to\": 4343, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4297, \"end\": 4304, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8195751452629179, \"rank\": 0.21322967228873763, \"text\": \"Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 4307, \"end\": 4312, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Police_of_The_Wire\", \"score\": 0.9999999954616214, \"rank\": 4.462229788014452e-09, \"text\": \"Elena\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Police_of_The_Wire\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Police_of_The_Wire\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the tide\", \"from\": 4190, \"to\": 4198}, {\"ngram\": \"the line\", \"from\": 4263, \"to\": 4271}, {\"ngram\": \"a penalty\", \"from\": 4333, \"to\": 4342}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This event has had its ups and downs, but I think it's here to stay now, there was no watching that here or at home who would not have loved it,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 4345, \"to\": 4501, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This event\", \"from\": 4346, \"to\": 4356}, {\"ngram\": \"its ups\", \"from\": 4365, \"to\": 4372}, {\"ngram\": \"downs\", \"from\": 4377, \"to\": 4382}, {\"ngram\": \"home\", \"from\": 4457, \"to\": 4461}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Some of the more traditional voices have called it silly but I think it's incredible.\", \"from\": 4503, \"to\": 4589, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the more traditional voices\", \"from\": 4512, \"to\": 4539}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The atmosphere was insane, and I enjoyed every single minute of it.\", \"from\": 4590, \"to\": 4657, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The atmosphere\", \"from\": 4590, \"to\": 4604}, {\"ngram\": \"every single minute\", \"from\": 4631, \"to\": 4650}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was way more emotional about the medal I got last week but it'll come together when I am wearing both around my neck later on.\", \"from\": 4659, \"to\": 4788, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the medal\", \"from\": 4691, \"to\": 4700}, {\"ngram\": \"my neck\", \"from\": 4771, \"to\": 4778}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The whole journey I have been on in the last ten years has been tough, it's been up and down.\", \"from\": 4790, \"to\": 4884, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The whole journey\", \"from\": 4791, \"to\": 4808}, {\"ngram\": \"the last ten years\", \"from\": 4827, \"to\": 4845}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Anyone who does sport at this level has bumps in the road so I am really proud of who I have been at thisOlympics.\\\"\", \"from\": 4885, \"to\": 5000, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Anyone\", \"from\": 4885, \"to\": 4891}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 4901, \"to\": 4906}, {\"ngram\": \"this level\", \"from\": 4910, \"to\": 4920}, {\"ngram\": \"bumps\", \"from\": 4925, \"to\": 4930}, {\"ngram\": \"the road\", \"from\": 4934, \"to\": 4942}, {\"ngram\": \"thisOlympics\", \"from\": 4986, \"to\": 4998}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Clarke and Woods both insisted they benefited from the installation of a big drop in ramp at their Lea Valley training base, made possible by National Lottery funding.\", \"from\": 5002, \"to\": 5169, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5144, \"end\": 5168, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Lottery_Community_Fund\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"National Lottery funding\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Lottery_Community_Fund\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Lottery_Community_Fund\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Clarke\", \"from\": 5002, \"to\": 5008}, {\"ngram\": \"Woods\", \"from\": 5013, \"to\": 5018}, {\"ngram\": \"the installation\", \"from\": 5053, \"to\": 5069}, {\"ngram\": \"a big drop\", \"from\": 5073, \"to\": 5083}, {\"ngram\": \"ramp\", \"from\": 5087, \"to\": 5091}, {\"ngram\": \"their Lea Valley training base\", \"from\": 5095, \"to\": 5125}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Woods also insisted she had no regrets about going for a late move against Australia's eventual gold medallist Noemie Fox.\", \"from\": 5171, \"to\": 5293, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5246, \"end\": 5255, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.8769496245901105, \"rank\": 0.13975088468637742, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 5282, \"end\": 5292, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noemie_Fox\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noemie Fox\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noemie_Fox\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noemie_Fox\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Woods\", \"from\": 5171, \"to\": 5176}, {\"ngram\": \"no regrets\", \"from\": 5199, \"to\": 5209}, {\"ngram\": \"a late move\", \"from\": 5226, \"to\": 5237}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was never going to play it safe, especially in an Olympic final,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 5295, \"to\": 5373, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an Olympic final\", \"from\": 5345, \"to\": 5361}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This happens once every four years and you never know whether this will be your last chance, I want to have no regrets.\", \"from\": 5374, \"to\": 5494, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your last chance\", \"from\": 5450, \"to\": 5466}, {\"ngram\": \"no regrets\", \"from\": 5483, \"to\": 5493}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am a brave person and I wanted to showcase that.\", \"from\": 5496, \"to\": 5547, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a brave person\", \"from\": 5502, \"to\": 5516}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I just got a bit tangled and could not get the pole around my head.\", \"from\": 5548, \"to\": 5615, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the pole\", \"from\": 5591, \"to\": 5599}, {\"ngram\": \"my head\", \"from\": 5607, \"to\": 5614}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I thought maybe I could get silver, but those girls really fought top to bottom.\\\"\", \"from\": 5616, \"to\": 5697, \"en